ᎴᎬᎾᎻ: "Plantae"
ᏆᎢᎳᎻ: "Magnoliophyta"
ᏗᎦᎪᏗ: "Magnoliopsida"
ᎣᎸᏙ: "Fagales"
ᏥᏓᎾᎷ: "Fagaceae"
ᎨᏄᏍ: "Quercus"

